  <summary date="2020-01-25T19:02:52Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Modernizing Obstetric Medicine Standards Act of 2019 or the MOMS Act

This bill requires the Health Resources and Services Administration to contract with a national organization to (1) develop best practices relating to maternal mortality and morbidity prevention, and (2) establish a grant program for states to implement such best practices.</summary>
